LD42 - Planet Runner



Sequence of events:
=============================================

-Start on earth
-Run off ramp to launch yourself into the air - This uses up energy
-Earn money for airtime, distance ran, space travelled and how many planets you land on
-Once you stop the player accesses the shop to upgrade their jumping, running and stamina
-To reach other planets you have to jump and travel through space until you get caught by a planet's
gravity field
-You must target yourself to the planet you want to go to when travelling in space
-If the player reaches a new planet they'll have to use that planet's ramp by running to it.



^                                                           ^
|                                                           |
-This process repeats until you reach the end of the universe
